author: sfgate.com
title: Horoscope for Saturday, 10/17/15 by Christopher Renstrom
text:
ARIES. (March 20 - April 19): A farfetched hope or high stakes project is realized when Mars conjoins Jupiter. These are the sensational, one-of-a-kind moments you live for!
TAURUS. (April 20 - May 20): You're entering a prosperous period. You don't have to squirrel away all the money that will be coming your way. You're allowed to spend some on yourself.
GEMINI. (May 21 - June 20): The Mars/Jupiter conjunction brings out your possessive side. It's a great relief to a certain someone who was beginning to wonder if you even cared.
CANCER. (June 21 - July 21): Call in all debts and favors. They do you no good collecting dust on the shelf. Every little bit helps right now.
LEO. (July 22 - Aug. 22): Push for what you want. You may not get everything you set your sights on, but it will be considerably more than you think.
VIRGO. (Aug. 23 - Sept. 22): Strong-arming someone may produce immediate results, but is it worth the unpleasantness? Try appealing to this person's spirit of cooperation instead. You'll get a lot further plus you'll be on speaking terms.
LIBRA. (Sept. 23 - Oct. 22): Things come together in the most extraordinary way between now and the 23d. It's a defining moment. Milk it for all its worth.
SCORPIO. (Oct. 23 - Nov. 21): Right now you have to be in your own corner. If you believe in what you're doing, then it doesn't matter what others think.
SAGITTARIUS. (Nov. 22 - Dec. 20): This is a time for focusing on tangibles. You can reap many benefits by paying attention to details.
CAPRICORN. (Dec. 21 - Jan. 19): Today you face a hurdle. Go back the way you came and wonder what if or take a running leap? You already know the answer.
AQUARIUS. (Jan. 20 - Feb. 17): An extraordinary Mars/Jupiter conjunction puts you in the black. It's time to pay back certain people before they see red.
PISCES. (Feb. 18 - March 19): The Mars/Jupiter conjunction shows you hooking a whopper of an opportunity. Is it too much to handle? You'll find out in the next few days.
